Snipp Interactive, Inc announces non-brokered private placement












Thursday, 21 Apr 2016 03:08pm EDT Snipp Interactive, Inc:Says Non-brokered private placement for gross proceeds of up to C$7.Says Financing will be comprised of up to 23,333,334 common shares at a market price of C$0.30 per Share.Net proceeds raised through the Financing will be used for product development, sales & marketing and general working capital purposes. 



